room_title: Escape room "Houdini's Lounge" by Escape This Norman in Oklahoma City
room_address: 550 24th Ave NW Suite C Norman, OK 73069
room_description: While touring the late, great escape artist Harry Houdini’s house which recently went up for sale in Harlem, you happen upon a mysterious doorway in the back of the house.  Upon entering, the door locks behind you and you become trapped inside his private lounge.  Can you escape Houdini’s tricks or will you be stuck inside the Escape Artist’s house forever??
